text.header1: Vula izixhumanisi Ngokuphepha nangokungaziwa usebenzisa i-Kasm Open-in-Isolation.
text.header2: Isandiso sesiphequluli se-Kasm Open in Isolation sinikeza inketho yemenyu yokuchofoza kwesokudla ukuze uvule izixhumanisi zewebhu kusiphequluli esisodwa sezindawo Zokusebenzela. Lokhu kwenza kube lula futhi kungabi nazihibe ukuvula ngokuphephile ama-URL asolisayo/angaphephile noma ukugcina ubumfihlo bakho. Njengoba ikhasi lewebhu linikezwa ngaphakathi kwesiphequluli sendawo yokusebenza ekude, kunokuba lisetshenziswe kukhompuyutha yakho yasendaweni, uyakwazi ukuxhumana ngokuphephile nangokungaziwa nekhasi lewebhu.
text.header3: Bona imibhalo ye-Kasm ukuze uthole imininingwane eyengeziwe.

title.tooltip1: I-Go izovula i-URL endaweni yokusebenza entsha, indlela yokhiye we-Cast ingeyendawo yokusebenza ekhona esebenzayo
title.tooltip2: Lapho uvula umbhalo kuseshini ye-Kasm Workspaces ngaphandle uma iyunithi yezinhlamvu iyi-URL evumelekile izodluliselwa enjinini yokusesha.
title.tooltip3: Uma uvula umbhalo Endaweni Yokusebenzela ungase ufune ukushintsha iyunithi yezinhlamvu ezidluliselwe kuNdawo Yokusebenzela (Thola isekela i-RegExp evamile enama-delimiters /regexp/g)
